t classes diversify even the most mature portfolio sustainable longterm inflationlinked cashflows predictable longterm cash flows typically with government backed revenues or capacity based contracts stable inflation linked revenues low market risk high operating margins relatively low ongoing variable operational and maintenance expenses high barriers to entry large capital requirements limiting the number of natural competitors strong operational experience needed to successfully manage assets provision of essential services foundation for basic irreplaceable public services sometimes regulated benefit from relatively inelastic demand ﻿ esg  basalt  home  esg basalt seeks to recognise esg at all stages of the investment lifecycle acquisitionmanagementdisposal and understand the impact that esg has on the long term performance of portfolio investments basalt recognises that effective research analysis and evaluation of esg issues are fundamental for driving value and performance of investments over the medium and longer term ﻿ our investments  basalt  home  our investments basalt focuses on the north american and european mid market infrastructure sectors of utility energy and transportation basalt is seeking low volatility assets that are either in the operational phase or in late stage construction projects that when complete exhibit traditional infrastructure characteristics basalt investments typically exhibit the following characteristics low volatility limited correlation with other asset classes operate on a largely uncorrelated cycle to other asset classes diversify even the most mature portfolio sustainable longterm inflationlinked cashflows predictable longterm cash flows typically with government backed revenues or capacity based contracts stable inflation linked revenues low market risk high operating margins relatively low ongoing variable operational and maintenance expenses high barriers to entry large capital requirements limiting the number of natu